rows.label: tlk42300011_03_msg0001
rows.name:
What kind of cylinder do you use
when you salvage, mo?

rows.label: tlk42300011_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Rimurimu understands the feeling of being reluctant
to buy a slightly more expensive cylinder, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300011_03_msg0003
rows.name:
But, but... the expensive cylinders are better
quality and you're more likely to get good things, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300011_03_msg0004
rows.name:
So when you have some extra money,
it's a good idea to take a chance and buy an
expensive one, mo.
